  "original_title": "\u0b8e\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0ba8\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd 5 \u0bb5\u0bc0\u0ba4\u0bae\u0bbe\u0ba9 \u0ba4\u0ba9\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bb8\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc7 \u0b9a\u0bc7\u0bb5\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b88\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd - \u0b87\u0bb2\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8 \u0ba4\u0ba9\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bb8\u0bcd \u0b89\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0bae\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbe\u0bb3\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bae\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Only 5 percent of private buses will be put into service in the coming days - Sri Lanka Private Bus Owners Association",
      "author": "Digital Desk 5",
      "body_lines": [
        "Due to fuel shortage, private buses will be plying at 5 per cent in the coming days.",
        "Kemunu Wijeratne, President of the Private Bus Owners Association of Sri Lanka, said that Transport Minister Bandula Gunawardena, who only paid attention to bus fares, should resign.",
        "He mentioned the above while attending a media conference in Colombo (01) on Friday.",
        "Buses are not generously compensated for the transport service but only bus fares have been increased unfairly.",
        "The current bus fare revision is seen to further affect the economically disadvantaged population.",
        "Bus fares were hiked five times in the last 6 months due to fuel price hike alone.",
        "The bus fare revision may have been done without paying attention to the fuel price hike in the annual bus fare revision.",
        "The Transport Minister did not pay attention to the demand to get fuel subsidy without increasing the bus fare.",
        "We urge the President and the Prime Minister to demand the resignation of Transport Minister Bandula Gunawardena.",
        "Due to fuel shortage, private buses accounted for 8 percent of the transport activity today.",
        "He said that in the coming days only 5 percent of the transport activity will be covered by private buses."
      ],
